  <brief_title>Safety of GANFORT® Ophthalmic Solution in Chinese Patients With Open-angle Glaucoma or Ocular Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Safety of GANFORT® (Bimatoprost 0.03% Plus Timolol 0.5%) Ophthalmic Solution in Chinese Patients With Open-angle Glaucoma or Ocular Hypertension</official_title>
  <sponsors>
