  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A study to evaluate the long-term safety of GANFORT® (bimatoprost 0.03% plus timolol 0.5%) in
      Chinese patients with open-angle glaucoma or ocular hypertension who are insufficiently
      responsive to topical beta-blocker or prostaglandin analogues.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
